        "content": "<p>108. 如何幫陣列元素設定非零的初始值？須寫出C++程式碼。</p>\r\n\r\n<p>本程式是使用迴圈來設定初始值</p>\r\n\r\n<p>#include &lt;iostream&gt;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>int main() {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; int arr[5];&nbsp; // 建立一個陣列<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; for (int i = 0; i &lt; 5; i++) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; arr[i] = i + 1;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; // 輸出陣列元素的值<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; for (int i = 0; i &lt; 5; i++) {<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; std::cout &lt;&lt; arr[i] &lt;&lt; &quot; &quot;;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; }<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; std::cout &lt;&lt; std::endl;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; return 0;<br />\r\n}</p>",
